eizures.', 'Synergism', 'The use of opioids in conjunction with benzodiazepines or other CNS depressants should generally be avoided unless alternative treatment options are inadequate.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/289577/', '', 'Naloxone, Naltrexone', '', 1767369485);
